Class Airplane

  • java.lang.Object
    • Airplane

  • public class Airplane
extends java.lang.Object
    This class represents an airplane with an (x,y) coordinate and velocities in the x and y direction
    Version:
    5/13/19
    Author:
    Ashwini Suriyaprakash, Rujuta Swadi
